	<h2>現在起，人人都可以出版</h2>
	<p>ContPub (continuous publishing) is the easiest way to publish your own books!</p>
	<p>ContPub （持續出版系統）是您自行出版專屬書籍的最簡易方式！</p>
	<ol>
		<li>Thinking</li>
		<li>Writing</li>
		<li>Publishing</li>
